      "transition": null,
      "trace": [],
      "chat": {
        "lineCount": 8776,
        "sha256": "804f1a0f45d0d00d4c13f003d3bb817b908b4c7d311d888da269f01f829ee82b",
        "raw": {
          "lineCount": 8776,
          "sha256": "0232aa58129056b3ac0a74a15e1833cafeb43e7816bb938705551e53e1ef815d",
          "head": [
            "",
            "\u001b[38;5;69m────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[39m",
            " \u001b[1m\u001b[38;5;109mWhat's New\u001b[39m\u001b[22m                                                                                         ",
            "",
            "                                                                                                    ",
            " \u001b[38;5;222m\u001b[1m[0.10.0] - 2025-11-25\u001b[22m\u001b[39m                                                                              ",
            "                                                                                                    ",
            " Initial public release.                                                                            ",
            "                                                                                                    ",
            " \u001b[38;5;222m\u001b[1m### \u001b[22m\u001b[39m\u001b[38;5;222m\u001b[1mAdded\u001b[22m\u001b[39m                                                                                          ",
            "                                                                                                    ",
            " \u001b[38;5;109m- \u001b[39mInteractive TUI with streaming responses                                                         ",
            " \u001b[38;5;109m- \u001b[39mConversation session management with \u001b[38;5;109m--continue\u001b[39m, \u001b[38;5;109m--resume\u001b[39m, and \u001b[38;5;109m--session\u001b[39m flags                   ",
            " \u001b[38;5;109m- \u001b[39mMulti-line input support (Shift+Enter or Option+Enter for new lines)                             ",
            " \u001b[38;5;109m- \u001b[39mTool execution: \u001b[38;5;109mread\u001b[39m, \u001b[38;5;109mwrite\u001b[39m, \u001b[38;5;109medit\u001b[39m, \u001b[38;5;109mbash\u001b[39m, \u001b[38;5;109mglob\u001b[39m, \u001b[38;5;109mgrep\u001b[39m, \u001b[38;5;109mthink\u001b[39m                                       ",
            " \u001b[38;5;109m- \u001b[39mThinking mode support for Claude with visual indicator and \u001b[38;5;109m/thinking\u001b[39m selector                    ",
            " \u001b[38;5;109m- \u001b[39mFile path autocompletion with \u001b[38;5;109m@\u001b[39m prefix                                                           ",
            " \u001b[38;5;109m- \u001b[39mSlash command autocompletion                                                                     ",
            " \u001b[38;5;109m- \u001b[39m\u001b[38;5;109m/export\u001b[39m command for HTML session export                                                          ",
            " \u001b[38;5;109m- \u001b[39m\u001b[38;5;109m/model\u001b[39m command for runtime model switching                                                       "
          ],
          "tail": [
            " \u001b[38;5;109m- \u001b[39mFixed messages queued during compaction to preserve steering and follow-up delivery behavior     ",
            "   (\u001b[38;5;109m\u001b[4m#6730\u001b[24m\u001b[39m\u001b[38;5;241m (https://github.com/earendil-works/pi/pull/6730)\u001b[39m by \u001b[38;5;109m\u001b[4m@dannote\u001b[24m\u001b[39m\u001b[38;5;241m                              ",
            "   \u001b[38;5;241m(https://github.com/dannote)\u001b[39m).                                                                   ",
            " \u001b[38;5;109m- \u001b[39mFixed read tool errors being syntax-highlighted as if they were file contents (\u001b[38;5;109m\u001b[4m#6731\u001b[24m\u001b[39m\u001b[38;5;241m             ",
            "   \u001b[38;5;241m(https://github.com/earendil-works/pi/pull/6731)\u001b[39m by \u001b[38;5;109m\u001b[4m@dannote\u001b[24m\u001b[39m\u001b[38;5;241m (https://github.com/dannote)\u001b[39m).      ",
            " \u001b[38;5;109m- \u001b[39mFixed llama.cpp router download progress updates and removed redundant wording from model action ",
            "   confirmations.                                                                                   ",
            " \u001b[38;5;109m- \u001b[39mMoved automatic model catalog network refresh out of startup initialization and into the running ",
            "   interactive and RPC modes.                                                                       ",
            " \u001b[38;5;109m- \u001b[39mFixed persisted sessions being read and parsed twice when opened, reducing startup latency for   ",
            "   large sessions (\u001b[38;5;109m\u001b[4m#6793\u001b[24m\u001b[39m\u001b[38;5;241m (https://github.com/earendil-works/pi/issues/6793)\u001b[39m).                       ",
            " \u001b[38;5;109m- \u001b[39mFixed prompt-template defaults for all arguments (\u001b[38;5;109m${@:-default}\u001b[39m and \u001b[38;5;109m${ARGUMENTS:-default}\u001b[39m)       ",
            "   (\u001b[38;5;109m\u001b[4m#6695\u001b[24m\u001b[39m\u001b[38;5;241m (https://github.com/earendil-works/pi/issues/6695)\u001b[39m).                                      ",
            " \u001b[38;5;109m- \u001b[39mFixed obsolete custom UI, custom tool, and custom editor examples in the extension documentation ",
            "   (\u001b[38;5;109m\u001b[4m#6735\u001b[24m\u001b[39m\u001b[38;5;241m (https://github.com/earendil-works/pi/issues/6735)\u001b[39m).                                      ",
            " \u001b[38;5;109m- \u001b[39mFixed Kimi Coding sessions to show API-equivalent implied costs with the subscription indicator. ",
            " \u001b[38;5;109m- \u001b[39mFixed OpenAI Responses early stream endings to trigger automatic retry instead of ending the     ",
            "   agent run (\u001b[38;5;109m\u001b[4m#6727\u001b[24m\u001b[39m\u001b[38;5;241m (https://github.com/earendil-works/pi/issues/6727)\u001b[39m).                            ",
            "                                                                                                    ",
            "\u001b[38;5;69m────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[39m"
          ]
        },
        "head": [
          "",
          "────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────",
          " What's New",
          "",
          "",
          " [0.10.0] - 2025-11-25",
          "",
          " Initial public release.",
          "",
          " ### Added",
          "",
          " - Interactive TUI with streaming responses",
          " - Conversation session management with --continue, --resume, and --session flags",
          " - Multi-line input support (Shift+Enter or Option+Enter for new lines)",
          " - Tool execution: read, write, edit, bash, glob, grep, think",
          " - Thinking mode support for Claude with visual indicator and /thinking selector",
          " - File path autocompletion with @ prefix",
          " - Slash command autocompletion",
          " - /export command for HTML session export",
          " - /model command for runtime model switching"
        ],
        "tail": [
          " - Fixed messages queued during compaction to preserve steering and follow-up delivery behavior",
          "   (#6730 (https://github.com/earendil-works/pi/pull/6730) by @dannote",
          "   (https://github.com/dannote)).",
          " - Fixed read tool errors being syntax-highlighted as if they were file contents (#6731",
          "   (https://github.com/earendil-works/pi/pull/6731) by @dannote (https://github.com/dannote)).",
          " - Fixed llama.cpp router download progress updates and removed redundant wording from model action",
          "   confirmations.",
          " - Moved automatic model catalog network refresh out of startup initialization and into the running",
          "   interactive and RPC modes.",
          " - Fixed persisted sessions being read and parsed twice when opened, reducing startup latency for",
          "   large sessions (#6793 (https://github.com/earendil-works/pi/issues/6793)).",
          " - Fixed prompt-template defaults for all arguments (${@:-default} and ${ARGUMENTS:-default})",
          "   (#6695 (https://github.com/earendil-works/pi/issues/6695)).",
          " - Fixed obsolete custom UI, custom tool, and custom editor examples in the extension documentation",
          "   (#6735 (https://github.com/earendil-works/pi/issues/6735)).",
          " - Fixed Kimi Coding sessions to show API-equivalent implied costs with the subscription indicator.",
          " - Fixed OpenAI Responses early stream endings to trigger automatic retry instead of ending the",
          "   agent run (#6727 (https://github.com/earendil-works/pi/issues/6727)).",
          "",
          "────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────"
        ]
      }
    },
